the feeling of diving into the sea.\n\nVirtual Reality\nYou can use VR devices to immerse yourself in a fantasy world and meditate.\n\nWhat are Solfeggio frequencies?\nMeditation mode incorporates Solfeggio frequencies, which are also used in sound therapy.\nAlso known as Nikola Tesla's 3-6-9 theory, it is said to be \"the key to the universe that holds the secrets of energy, vibration, and resonance.\"\nIn sound therapy, it is used to reduce mental stress, have a healing effect, increase motivation, and restore mental strength.\nThe famous frequencies of 396Hz, 417Hz, and 528Hz are also mixed, as well as other Solfeggio frequencies.", "short_description": "Solfeggio frequency meditation to improve concentration and memory.\nAim for a high score with brain training.\nA fantastic stage inspired by the deep sea.\nYou can meditate while experiencing the feeling of diving into the sea.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sbluedot1.wixsite.com/bluedot-studio/privacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "BlueDot Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sbluedot1.wixsite.com/bluedot-studio", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "810139357995560"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ja", "ko", "zh_CN", "zh_HK", "zh_TW", "it", "es", "pt", "ru", "uk", "de"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7953340781368023"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "P